98
00:06:21,297 --> 00:06:24,175
SCUM IS BETTER OFF DEAD,
JUSTICE SERVED, NICE!

99
00:06:30,389 --> 00:06:31,390
Darn it.

100
00:06:43,528 --> 00:06:45,029
